<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to TripSync!</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        body, h1, p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        /* Main styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to TripSync - Your Ultimate Travel Companion!</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>
        <p>Welcome aboard to TripSync, your ultimate travel companion! We're thrilled to have you join our community of adventurers, explorers, and wanderlust souls. Get ready to embark on unforgettable journeys, discover new destinations, and create lasting memories.</p>
        <p>Here's a quick guide to get you started on your travel journey with TripSync:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Explore Exciting Destinations: Dive into our curated list of destinations, from bustling cities to serene beaches, and find your next travel adventure.</li>
            <li>Plan Your Perfect Trip: Use our intuitive trip planning tools to create personalized itineraries tailored to your preferences and interests.</li>
            <li>Discover Hidden Gems: Unlock insider tips, hidden gems, and local recommendations from fellow travelers to make the most out of your trip.</li>
            <li>Book with Confidence: Enjoy seamless booking experiences with our trusted partners, ensuring convenience and peace of mind every step of the way.</li>
            <li>Stay Connected: Join our vibrant community of travelers, share your experiences, and connect with like-minded individuals from around the globe.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>As a token of our appreciation for joining TripSync, here's a special discount code <strong>[CODE]</strong> for your next booking. Simply enter the code at checkout to redeem your offer!</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, suggestions, or simply want to share your travel experiences, feel free to reach out to our dedicated support team at <a href="mailto:support@tripsync.com">support@tripsync.com</a>. We're here to assist you every step of the way.</p>
        <p>Once again, welcome to TripSync! Get ready to embark on unforgettable adventures and make memories that will last a lifetime.</p>
        <p>Happy travels!</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The TripSync Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
